Title: Rudiments of Holography
Authors: Enrique Alvarez, Jorge Conde and Lorenzo Hernandez
Comments: 60 pages, additional misprints corrected, references added
Report-no: IFT-UAM/CSIC-02-05
\\
  An elementary introduction to Maldacena's AdS/CFT correspondence is given,
with some emphasis in the Fefferman-Graham construction. This is based on
lectures given by one of us (E.A.) at the Universidad Autonoma de Madrid.
